sub_title: Freelance Event and On Location Portrait Photographer
summary:
I’m a passionate and enthusiastic event and portrait photographer who focuses on capturing the memorable essence of each event and on creating unique and personalized visuals.  
I offer imagery with a vibrant twist to my clients. Over the years, I've developed a style of imagery that has real heart & soul. 
My goal is to help people building their image, authentically, and bring a story to life with creative and thoughtful photos. 

I am a very determined, dedicated, dynamic and enthusiastic person who really enjoys communicating at all levels and I am particularly comfortable dealing with people. My previous experiences have left me with a genuine passion for customer satisfaction and marketing. 

- Branding/ Lifestyle in-house corporate photo report
- Corporate Events
- Parties and celebrations
- Theater/ Dance 
- Private Parties
- Weddings
- Portraits
- Image post-production Lightroom/Photoshop
